sops.sop:
**Workflow:**
User -> Planner;
Planner -> WebBrowser (Life Sciences);
Planner -> WebBrowser (Health Sciences);
WebBrowser (Life Sciences) -> CalculationAgent;
WebBrowser (Health Sciences) -> CalculationAgent;
CalculationAgent -> Summarizer;
Summarizer -> End.

**Description:**
1. Planner creates execution plans for Life Sciences and Health Sciences data collection.
2. WebBrowser navigates ScienceDirect to extract Reference Works counts for both domains, filtering out 2023+ entries.
3. CalculationAgent computes sample standard deviations, finds the difference, and rounds to 3 decimal places.
4. Summarizer delivers the final numerical answer.
